{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":240,"createTime":"2019-06-03 10:25:07","topicId":null,"tagId":48,"rule":4,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p style=\"line-height:24px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">咳嗽与咳痰</span></strong></p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、病因诱因：有无呼吸道、胸膜、心血管疾病？有无服血管紧张素转换酶剂？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、主要症状特点：咳嗽性质（干性？湿性？）程度？时间与节律（清晨起床或体位改变时加剧？）咳嗽的音色？痰的颜色、性状、气味、痰量？咳痰与体位的关系？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、伴随症状：有无发热、胸痛、呼吸困难、咯血？怀疑支气管扩张时要注意有无杵状指。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、全身状态：发病以来饮食、睡眠、大小便及体重变化</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、诊疗经过：发病以来是否到医院检查过，曾做过哪些检查和治疗？（胸部片、CT）治疗是否有效？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、相关病史：(1)有无药物过敏史、手术史</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">(2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">既往有无类似病史？既往有无百日咳、麻疹、支气管肺炎、支气管哮喘、结核病等病史和吸烟史？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"","topic":null,"options":[],"tags":[{"id":48,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 13:45:34","updateTime":"2019-06-01 13:45:34","name":"咳嗽咳痰","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":15},{"id":286,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 16:03:29","updateTime":"2019-06-01 16:03:29","name":"咳嗽咳痰","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":19}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}